 which is larger than the previous space, 

00:02:18.680 --> 00:02:24.160
 because this hole was not the diagonal, but the sum of those two sides. 

00:02:24.220 --> 00:02:25.760
 And if you still remember Pythagoras, 

00:02:25.780 --> 00:02:29.400
 you have received an extra square root factor of 2, which is slightly more than 40%. 

